title: Haydn - The Complete String Quartets (22 CDs)
description:
Music : Classical : Lossless


This is a compilation of Joseph Haydn's complete String Quartets encoded in secure mode to FLAC. 

The performances were carried out by the Aeolian String Quartet (Emanuel Hurwitz, Raymond Keenlyside on violin, Margaret Major on viola, and Derek Simpson on cello) for the London label.


Inside this CD are:
-10 Early Quartets Op 0 - 0p 2
- 6 Quartets Op.9 -- 6 Quartets Op. 17 -- 6 Quartets Op.20 --
- 6 Quartets Op.33 -- Quartet Op.42 -- 6 Quartets Op.50
- The Seven Last Words of our Saviour on the Cross Op.51
- 3 Quartets Op.54 -- 3 Quartets Op.55 -- 6 Quartets Op.64
- 3 Quartets Op.71 -- 3 Quartets Op.74 -- 6 Quartets Op.76
- 2 Quartets Op.77 -- Quartet fragment Op.103 (Haydn's unfinished Quartet)

There are a total of 340 files in 22 separate folders. All files have already been named according to booklet information. I'm sorry, I don't have a scanner for the booklets and covers, and the digital camera didn't work too well either.

The playlist and log files show the order of the songs on the CD's.


Happy downloading and enjoy!
